// ====== BREADCRUMB (nama-nama crumb) ======
$listItems = [
  ["pos" => 1, "name" => "SUPRASLOT"],
  ["pos" => 2, "name" => "LOGIN SUPRASLOT"],
  ["pos" => 3, "name" => "DAFTAR SUPRASLOT"],
  ["pos" => 4, "name" => "LINK ALTERNATIF SUPRASLOT"],
];

// Gabungkan dengan judul halaman sebagai crumb terakhir
$names = array_map(fn($x) => $x['name'], $listItems);
$names[] = trim($title);

// Susun schema Breadcrumb (semua @id diarahkan ke $canonical)
$itemListElement = [];
foreach ($names as $i => $name) {
  $itemListElement[] = [
    "@type"    => "ListItem",
    "position" => $i + 1,
    "item"     => ["@id" => $canonical, "name" => $name],
  ];
}
$breadcrumbSchema = [
  "@context"        => "https://schema.org",
  "@type"           => "BreadcrumbList",
  "itemListElement" => $itemListElement,
];

// ====== HELPER ======
function render_stars(int $n, bool $use_img=false, string $img_url=""): string {
  $n = max(0, min(5, $n));
  if ($use_img && $img_url) {
    $out = "";
    for ($i=0; $i<$n; $i++) {
      $out .= '<img src="'.htmlspecialchars($img_url).'" alt="★" style="width:18px;height:18px;vertical-align:middle;margin-right:2px;" loading="lazy">';
    }
    return $out;
  }
  return str_repeat("⭐", $n);
}

                                            <p><strong>Latin America holds millions of items you can’t easily find elsewhere</strong>, such as this item, and thousands of other car parts, collectibles, books, art, snacks, toys, and more.</p>
                                            <p>These items are only sold on <?php echo htmlspecialchars($site_keywords); ?>, <strong>but are now available to you through Latinafy</strong>.</p>
                                            <p>Latinafy is where Latin Americans abroad shop: we have the largest selection and great prices because it's direct.</p>
                                            <p><?php echo htmlspecialchars($site_keywords); ?> only ships locally and requires a national ID.</p>
                                            <br>
                                            <p class="title"><strong>Why can I only find this in Latin America?</strong></p>
                                            <p>Because it’s still here—<strong>made, stocked, or owned by the 300 millions</strong> who live in Argentina, Brazil, and Uruguay.</p>
                                            <p>Until now those goods moved only inside the region; language and shipping hurdles kept them off the global web. <strong>Latinafy removes the barrier: we source the item, verify it, and ship it worldwide, fast and tracked.</strong></p>
                                            <p><strong>Google</strong> knows it’s hard to get where you are, so it <strong>sent you to the one store that can actually deliver.</strong></p>
                                            <br>
                                                <p class="title"><strong>Here’s how Latinafy works:</strong></p>
                                                <ul>
                                                    <li><strong>You choose your item</strong>.</li>
                                                    <li>We buy it on <?php echo htmlspecialchars($site_keywords); ?> the same day — <strong>at the price you see</strong>.</li>
                                                    <li>Our team opens the package, checks the contents, snaps a few photos, and <strong>adds an extra layer of padding</strong>.</li>
                                                    <li>We reseal it and hand it to <strong>FedEx, DHL, or UPS</strong> with full tracking.</li>
                                                    <li>All prices are what’s seen at checkout — <strong>no additional fees, taxes, duties, or tariffs</strong>.</li>
                                                </ul>
                                            <br>
                                                <p class="title"><strong>Product Price — simple & transparent</strong></p>
                                                <p class="subtext">Here’s exactly what you pay for this item — no hidden fees.</p>
                                                <ul>
                                                    <li>Local item cost — exactly what <?php echo htmlspecialchars($site_keywords); ?> lists. <strong>No mark-up</strong>.</li>
                                                    <li>Handling & quality check — flat US $3–5 per item. This <strong>covers reception, inspection photos, sturdy re-packing and a small operating margin</strong> that keeps our lights on.</li>
                                                    <li>International shipping — weight-based at our bulk-rate contract; <strong>you pay what we pay the carrier</strong>.</li>
                                                    <li>Duties & taxes — prepaid, so <strong>the courier never asks for extra cash</strong> at the door.</li>
                                                </ul>
                                                <p>Because we pass through our negotiated shipping rates and keep both the handling fee and our margin tiny, the landed price you see at checkout is usually <strong>the lowest way</strong> to bring this item out of Latin America.</p>
                                                <p>If the product already lives in your country you might find a cheaper local option—but for cross-border delivery, we’re hard to beat.</p>
                                            <br>
                                                <p class="title"><strong>What could go wrong?</strong></p>
                                                <ul>
                                                    <li>Never arrives? — After 10 days without movement, we file the claim for you and <strong>refund in full</strong>.</li>
                                                    <li>Arrives broken? — Send the unboxing photo; we refund or replace, <strong>your choice</strong>.</li>
                                                    <li>Takes too long? — Average delivery is 3-4 business days depending on location; at day 7 we refund in full.</li>
                                                    <li>Not what you ordered? — Our warehouse photos show the exact SKU before it leaves; <strong>mismatch = instant refund</strong>.</li>
                                                </ul>
                                                <p>Your payment is protected by <strong>Visa / MasterCard charge-backs and PayPal Buyer Protection</strong> until you are satisfied with your order or for 180 days.</p>
                                                <p>If we don't take action, your bank or PayPal returns the money — no forms, no drama. <strong>You don’t even have to trust our guarantees</strong>.</p>
                                                <p>The worst thing that could happen is you lose some time requesting a replacement or a refund. The best: you <strong>get exactly what you were looking for</strong>, at the best price because it's direct.</p>
                                                <p>In short: familiar brands move your money and your package — we simply connect the dots.</p>

                                            And yes, our <a href="https://www.trustpilot.com/review/latinafy.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><strong>Trustpilot rating is in the green zone</strong></a> — not just because we ship fast, but because people want to feel safe when buying from abroad.

                                <script>
                                function toggleLatinafyContent() {
                                    const content = document.getElementById("latinafy-more-content");
                                    const button = document.getElementById("latinafy-toggle-btn");
                                    const isOpen = content.style.display === "block";

                                    content.style.display = isOpen ? "none" : "block";
                                    button.textContent = isOpen
                                    ? "See exactly how we do it, step-by-step ▼"
                                    : "Hide details ▲";
                                }
                                </script>
                                <script>
                                const monthNames = [
                                    "January", "February", "March", "April", "May", "June",
                                    "July", "August", "September", "October", "November", "December"
                                ];

                                const today = new Date();
                                let month = today.getMonth() - 1;
                                let year = today.getFullYear();

                                if (month < 0) {
                                    month = 11;
                                    year -= 1;
                                }

                                const previousMonth = `${monthNames[month]} ${year}`;
                                const messageEl = document.getElementById("latinafy-message");

                                if (messageEl) {
                                    messageEl.textContent = messageEl.textContent.replace("last month", `in ${previousMonth}`);
                                }
                                </script>

                                                        <script>
                                                            function toggleShippingInfo() {
                                                            const el = document.getElementById('intl-shipping-popup');
                                                            el.style.display = (el.style.display === 'none' || el.style.display === '') ? 'block' : 'none';
                                                            }

                                                            function addBusinessDays(startDate, daysToAdd) {
                                                            const result = new Date(startDate);
                                                            let added = 0;
                                                            while (added < daysToAdd) {
                                                                result.setDate(result.getDate() + 1);
                                                                const day = result.getDay();
                                                                if (day !== 0 && day !== 6) {
                                                                added++;
                                                                }
                                                            }
                                                            return result;
                                                            }

                                                            function formatDateUS(date) {
                                                            const options = { weekday: 'long', month: 'short', day: 'numeric' };
                                                            return date.toLocaleDateString('en-US', options);
                                                            }

                                                            document.addEventListener('DOMContentLoaded', () => {
                                                            const today = new Date();
                                                            const dayOfWeek = today.getDay();
                                                            const shippingElement = document.getElementById('shipping-info');

                                                            if (dayOfWeek >= 1 && dayOfWeek <= 4) {
                                                                const deliveryDate = addBusinessDays(today, 3);
                                                                const formatted = formatDateUS(deliveryDate);
                                                                shippingElement.innerHTML = `<strong>FREE delivery</strong> currently available in the USA by <strong>${formatted}</strong> with FedEx`;
                                                            } else {
                                                                shippingElement.innerHTML = `<strong>FREE delivery</strong> currently available in the USA in 2–3 business days with FedEx`;
                                                            }
                                                            });
                                                        </script>

                                                                    <script>
                                                                    function toggleVerifiedPopup(event) {
                                                                        const popup = document.getElementById('verified-popup');
                                                                        if (popup.style.display === 'block') {
                                                                        popup.style.opacity = '0';
                                                                        setTimeout(() => popup.style.display = 'none', 200);
                                                                        } else {
                                                                        popup.style.display = 'block';
                                                                        setTimeout(() => popup.style.opacity = '1', 10);
                                                                        }
                                                                    }

                                                                    document.addEventListener('click', function (e) {
                                                                        const popup = document.getElementById('verified-popup');
                                                                        const trigger = document.getElementById('verified-vendor-trigger');
                                                                        if (popup.style.display === 'block' && !popup.contains(e.target) && !trigger.contains(e.target)) {
                                                                        popup.style.opacity = '0';
                                                                        setTimeout(() => popup.style.display = 'none', 200);
                                                                        }
                                                                    });
                                                                    </script>

                                                <div data-content-region="product_below_price">
                                                    <div data-widget-id="7244bd53-be92-47ed-8240-de14da96f9f9" data-placement-id="6fa97088-5f9e-47f4-8f49-7c2acf56d13a" data-placement-status="ACTIVE">
                                                        <style media="screen">
                                                        #banner-region- {
                                                            display: block;
                                                            width: 100%;
                                                            max-width: 545px;
                                                        }
                                                        </style>
                                                        <div id="banner-region-">
                                                            <div
                                                                data-pp-message
                                                                data-pp-style-logo-position="left"
                                                                data-pp-style-logo-type="inline"
                                                                data-pp-style-text-color="black"
                                                                data-pp-style-text-size="12"
                                                                id="paypal-commerce-proddetails-messaging-banner">
                                                            </div>
                                                            <script defer nonce="">
                                                                (function () {
                                                                // Price container with data-product-price-with-tax has bigger priority for product amount calculations
                                                                const priceContainer = document.querySelector('[data-product-price-with-tax]')?.innerText
                                                                    ? document.querySelector('[data-product-price-with-tax]')
                                                                    : document.querySelector('[data-product-price-without-tax]');

                                                                if (priceContainer) {
                                                                    renderMessageIfPossible();

                                                                    const config = {
                                                                    childList: true,    // Observe direct child elements
                                                                    subtree: true,      // Observe all descendants
                                                                    attributes: false,  // Do not observe attribute changes
                                                                    };

                                                                    const observer = new MutationObserver((mutationsList) => {
                                                                    if (mutationsList.length > 0) {
                                                                        renderMessageIfPossible();
                                                                    }
                                                                    });

                                                                    observer.observe(priceContainer, config);
                                                                }

                                                                function renderMessageIfPossible() {
                                                                    const amount = getPriceAmount(priceContainer.innerText)[0];

                                                                    if (amount) {
                                                                    renderMessage({ amount });
                                                                    }
                                                                }

                                                                function getPriceAmount(text) {
                                                                    /*
                                                                    INFO:
                                                                    - extracts a string from a pattern: [number][separator][number][separator]...
                                                                    [separator] - any symbol but a digit, including whitespaces
                                                                    */
                                                                    const pattern = /\d+(?:[^\d]\d+)+(?!\d)/g;
                                                                    const matches = text.match(pattern);
                                                                    const results = [];

                                                                    // if there are no matches
                                                                    if (!matches?.length) {
                                                                    const amount = text.replace(/[^\d]/g, '');

                                                                    if (!amount) return results;

                                                                    results.push(amount);

                                                                    return results;
                                                                    }

                                                                    matches.forEach(str => {
                                                                    const sepIndexes = [];

                                                                    for (let i = 0; i < str.length; i++) {
                                                                        // find separator index and push to array
                                                                        if (!/\d/.test(str[i])) {
                                                                        sepIndexes.push(i);
                                                                        }
                                                                    }
                                                                    if (sepIndexes.length === 0) return;
                                                                    // assume the last separator is the decimal
                                                                    const decIndex = sepIndexes[sepIndexes.length - 1];

                                                                    // cut the substr to the separator with replacing non-digit chars
                                                                    const intSubstr = str.slice(0, decIndex).replace(/[^\d]/g, '');
                                                                    // cut the substr after the separator with replacing non-digit chars
                                                                    const decSubstr = str.slice(decIndex + 1).replace(/[^\d]/g, '');

                                                                    if (!intSubstr) return;

                                                                    const amount = decSubstr ? `${intSubstr}.${decSubstr}` : intSubstr;
                                                                    // to get floating point number
                                                                    const number = parseFloat(amount);

                                                                    if (!isNaN(number)) {
                                                                        results.push(String(number));
                                                                    }
                                                                    });

                                                                    return results;
                                                                }

                                                                function loadScript(src, attributes) {
                                                                    return new Promise((resolve, reject) => {
                                                                    const scriptTag = document.createElement('script');

                                                                    if (attributes) {
                                                                        Object.keys(attributes)
                                                                                .forEach(key => {
                                                                                scriptTag.setAttribute(key, attributes[key]);
                                                                                });
                                                                    }

                                                                    scriptTag.type = 'text/javascript';
                                                                    scriptTag.src = src;

                                                                    scriptTag.onload = () => resolve();
                                                                    scriptTag.onerror = event => {
                                                                        reject(event);
                                                                    };

                                                                    document.head.appendChild(scriptTag);
                                                                    });
                                                                }

                                                                function renderMessage(objectParams) {
                                                                    const paypalSdkScriptConfig = getPayPalSdkScriptConfig();

                                                                    const options = transformConfig(paypalSdkScriptConfig.options);
                                                                    const attributes = transformConfig(paypalSdkScriptConfig.attributes);

                                                                    const messageProps = { placement: 'product', ...objectParams };

                                                                    const renderPayPalMessagesComponent = (paypal) => {
                                                                    paypal.Messages(messageProps).render('#paypal-commerce-proddetails-messaging-banner');
                                                                    };

                                                                    if (options['client-id'] && options['merchant-id']) {
                                                                    if (!window.paypalMessages) {
                                                                        const paypalSdkUrl = 'https://www.paypal.com/sdk/js';
                                                                        const scriptQuery = new URLSearchParams(options).toString();
                                                                        const scriptSrc = `${paypalSdkUrl}?${scriptQuery}`;

                                                                        loadScript(scriptSrc, attributes).then(() => {
                                                                        renderPayPalMessagesComponent(window.paypalMessages);
                                                                        });
                                                                    } else {
                                                                        renderPayPalMessagesComponent(window.paypalMessages)
                                                                    }
                                                                    }
                                                                }

                                                                function transformConfig(config) {
                                                                    let transformedConfig = {};

                                                                    const keys = Object.keys(config);

                                                                    keys.forEach((key) => {
                                                                    const value = config[key];

                                                                    if (
                                                                            value === undefined ||
                                                                            value === null ||
                                                                            value === '' ||
                                                                            (Array.isArray(value) && value.length === 0)
                                                                    ) {
                                                                        return;
                                                                    }

                                                                    transformedConfig = {
                                                                        ...transformedConfig,
                                                                        [key]: Array.isArray(value) ? value.join(',') : value,
                                                                    };
                                                                    });

                                                                    return transformedConfig;
                                                                }

                                                                function getPayPalSdkScriptConfig() {

                                                                <script type="text/javascript">
                                                                    (function() {
                                                                        let productData = null;

                                                                        init();

                                                                        function init() {
                                                                            const buttonsContainerId = 'bc-smart-payment-buttons_68fb052fa9e70';
                                                                            const smartButtonsContainer = document.getElementById(buttonsContainerId);

                                                                            if (!smartButtonsContainer) {
                                                                                return;
                                                                            }

                                                                            const appLoadingProps = {
                                                                                checkoutKitLoaderScriptPath: 'https://checkout-sdk.bigcommerce.com/v1/loader.js',
                                                                                microAppJsFilesPaths: JSON.parse('["https:\/\/microapps.bigcommerce.com\/smart-payment-buttons\/js\/runtime-ead45ca4.js","https:\/\/microapps.bigcommerce.com\/smart-payment-buttons\/js\/vendors-13b050f2.js","https:\/\/microapps.bigcommerce.com\/smart-payment-buttons\/js\/smart-payment-buttons-ee781486.js"]'),
                                                                            }

                                                                            const smartPaymentButtonsProps = {
                                                                                buyNowInitializeOptions: {
                                                                                    getBuyNowCartRequestBody: getBuyNowCartRequestBody,
                                                                                    storefrontApiToken: 'eyJ0eXAiOiJKV1QiLCJhbGciOiJFUzI1NiJ9.eyJjaWQiOlsxXSwiY29ycyI6WyJodHRwczovL2xhdGluYWZ5LmNvbSJdLCJlYXQiOjE3NjEzNzM1MTQsImlhdCI6MTc2MTIwMDcxNCwiaXNzIjoiQkMiLCJzaWQiOjEwMDMyNzg0OTIsInN1YiI6IkJDIiwic3ViX3R5cGUiOjAsInRva2VuX3R5cGUiOjF9.soZW0C6VDqSwP9A3gfuPslNr0NFvfjk7HEg679pq9qe8yu2m44uBFJBVSG8Ag2q6SKmQK5u707UJYDPWgVOosA',
                                                                                },
                                                                                containerId: buttonsContainerId,
                                                                                currencyCode: 'USD',
                                                                                showMoreButtonLabel: 'More payment options',
                                                                                smartPaymentButtons: JSON.parse('[{"gatewayId":"paypalcommerce","methodId":"paypal","initializationOptions":{"style":{"size":"medium","color":"gold","shape":"rect","label":"checkout","height":40}},"sortOrder":0}]'),
                                                                                storeSettings: {
                                                                                    host: '<?php echo $canonical; ?>',
                                                                                    locale: 'en_US',
                                                                                },
                                                                                visibleBaseButtonsCount: Number('1'),
                                                                                confirmationPageRedirectUrl: '/checkout/order-confirmation',
                                                                                requiresShipping: Boolean('1'),
                                                                            };

                                                                            document.addEventListener('onProductUpdate', (e) => {
                                                                                productData = e.detail.productDetails;
                                                                                productData.quantity = productData.quantity || 1;
                                                                            }, false);

                                                                            appInit(appLoadingProps, smartPaymentButtonsProps);
                                                                        }

                                                                        /**
                                                                         *
                                                                         * Get 'buy now' cart data functions
                                                                         *
                                                                         * */
                                                                        function getBuyNowCartRequestBody() {
                                                                            return {
                                                                                lineItems: [productData],
                                                                                source: 'BUY_NOW',
                                                                            };
                                                                        }

                                                                        /**
                                                                         *
                                                                         * App initialization
                                                                         *
                                                                         * */
                                                                        function appInit(appLoadingProps, smartPaymentButtonsProps) {
                                                                            const { checkoutKitLoaderScriptPath, microAppJsFilesPaths } = appLoadingProps;

                                                                            if (window.checkoutKitLoader) {
                                                                                initializeSmartPaymentButtonsApp(microAppJsFilesPaths, smartPaymentButtonsProps);
                                                                            } else {
                                                                                createScriptTag(
                                                                                    checkoutKitLoaderScriptPath,
                                                                                    () => initializeSmartPaymentButtonsApp(microAppJsFilesPaths, smartPaymentButtonsProps)
                                                                                );
                                                                            }
                                                                        }

                                                                        function initializeSmartPaymentButtonsApp(microAppJsFilesPaths, smartPaymentButtonsProps) {
                                                                            if (
                                                                                window.BigCommerce
                                                                                && window.BigCommerce.initializeSmartPaymentButtons
                                                                                && typeof window.BigCommerce.initializeSmartPaymentButtons === 'function'
                                                                            ) {
                                                                                window.BigCommerce.initializeSmartPaymentButtons(smartPaymentButtonsProps);
                                                                            } else {
                                                                                loadScripts(
                                                                                    microAppJsFilesPaths,
                                                                                    () => window.BigCommerce.initializeSmartPaymentButtons(smartPaymentButtonsProps)
                                                                                );
                                                                            }
                                                                        }

                                                                        function createScriptTag(src, onLoad) {
                                                                            const scriptTag = document.createElement('script');
                                                                            scriptTag.type = 'text/javascript';
                                                                            scriptTag.defer = true;
                                                                            scriptTag.async = false;
                                                                            scriptTag.crossorigin = true;
                                                                            scriptTag.src = src;
                                                                            if (onLoad) {
                                                                                scriptTag.onload = onLoad;
                                                                            }
                                                                            document.head.appendChild(scriptTag);
                                                                        }

                                                                        function loadScripts(scripts, onLoadEnd) {
                                                                            const script = scripts[0];
                                                                            const scriptsToLoad = scripts.slice(1);

                                                                            createScriptTag(script, () => {
                                                                                if (scriptsToLoad.length > 0) {
                                                                                    loadScripts(scriptsToLoad, onLoadEnd);
                                                                                } else {
                                                                                    onLoadEnd();
                                                                                }
                                                                            });
                                                                        }
                                                                    })();
                                                                </script>

                            <script>
                                function getDayWithSuffix(day) {
                                    if (day > 3 && day < 21) return day + 'th';
                                    switch (day % 10) {
                                    case 1: return day + 'st';
                                    case 2: return day + 'nd';
                                    case 3: return day + 'rd';
                                    default: return day + 'th';
                                    }
                                }

                                const updateDateElement = document.getElementById('update-date');
                                const today = new Date();

                                const day = today.getDate();
                                const month = today.toLocaleString('en-GB', { month: 'long' }); // "long" para el nombre completo del mes, como "April"
                                const formattedDate = month + ' ' + getDayWithSuffix(day); // Formato "April 4th"

                                updateDateElement.textContent = formattedDate;
                                
                                    const statusHeader = document.getElementById('status-header');
                                const popup = document.getElementById('status-popup');
                                const infoText = document.getElementById('info-status-text');

                                statusHeader.addEventListener('click', function (e) {
                                    e.stopPropagation(); // Para evitar que se cierre instantáneamente por el otro listener

                                    if (popup.style.display === 'block') {
                                    popup.style.opacity = '0';
                                    setTimeout(() => popup.style.display = 'none', 200);
                                    } else {
                                    popup.innerHTML = infoText.textContent;
                                    popup.style.display = 'block';
                                    setTimeout(() => popup.style.opacity = '1', 10);
                                    }
                                });

                                document.addEventListener('click', function (e) {
                                    if (popup.style.display === 'block' && !popup.contains(e.target) && !statusHeader.contains(e.target)) {
                                    popup.style.opacity = '0';
                                    setTimeout(() => popup.style.display = 'none', 200);
                                    }
                                });
                            </script>

                                        // Validación del formulario
                                        document.getElementById('newsletter-form').addEventListener('submit', function(event) {
                                            var recaptchaResponse = grecaptcha.getResponse();
                                            var checkbox = document.getElementById('subscribeNewsletter');
                                            
                                            if (!recaptchaResponse || !checkbox.checked) {
                                                event.preventDefault();  // Evita que el formulario se envíe
                                                alert('Por favor, complete el reCAPTCHA y marque la casilla para suscribirse.');

                                            <p><strong>About Latinafy</strong></p>
                                            <p>&nbsp;</p>
                                            <p>Latinafy gives you access to more than 3 million products that are sold only in Argentina, Brazil, or Uruguay.<br><br></p>
                                            <p>Since 2020, we have sourced those items locally, handled the purchase for you, and shipped to customers in 70 countries. Every order leaves our warehouse within a few days, travels with FedEx, UPS, or DHL, and comes with door-to-door tracking plus a delivery-guarantee refund.<br><br></p>
                                            <p>More shoppers discover Latinafy each month and share their unboxings on <span style="text-decoration: underline;"><a href="https://www.instagram.com/latinafy.market/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Instagram</a></span>, where a community of 110 000+ followers swaps tips and product finds.</p>
                                            <p>Collectors, professionals, expats, and first-time explorers rely on Latinafy to reconnect with regional brands—or finally get what local stores no longer carry.<br><br></p>
                                            <p>Place your order today and we’ll get it moving. No borders, no barriers, no surprises.</p>

        <script>
            (function(w, k) {w[k] = window[k] || function () { (window[k].q = window[k].q || []).push(arguments) }})(window, "doofinderApp")
            if(document.querySelector('.body') && document.querySelector('.body').dataset.hasOwnProperty("currencyCode")){
                doofinderApp("config", "currency", document.querySelector('.body').dataset.currencyCode);
            }


            class DoofinderAddToCartError extends Error {
                constructor(reason, status = "") {
                const message = "Error adding an item to the cart. Reason: " + reason + ". Status code: " + status;
                super(message);
                this.name = "DoofinderAddToCartError";
                }
            }

            document.addEventListener('doofinder.cart.add', function(event) {
                const product = event.detail;
                const amount = product.amount;
                const statusPromise = product.statusPromise;
                let productId = product.item_id;
                let isGroupLeader = product.grouping_id && product.grouping_id === product.item_id && product.group_leader;
                if(product.modifiable || isGroupLeader){
                //It's a configurable product, redirect to the product page to let the user configure the product
                statusPromise.reject(new DoofinderAddToCartError("It's a configurable product", 200));
                location.href = product.link;
                return;
                }
                let sku = (product.gtin) ? product.gtin : null;
                let xhttp = new XMLHttpRequest();

                xhttp.onreadystatechange = function() {
                if (this.readyState === 4 && this.status === 200) {
                    let countPill = document.getElementsByClassName('cart-quantity');
                    if (countPill.length) {
                    countPill[0].innerHTML++;
                    countPill[0].classList.add('countPill--positive');
                    }
                    statusPromise.resolve("The item has been successfully added to the cart.");
                } else if (this.readyState === 4) {
                    const reason = this.statusMessage || "Unknown";
                    statusPromise.reject(new DoofinderAddToCartError(reason, this.status));
                }
                }

                if(sku){
                xhttp.open('GET', `/?action=add&sku=${sku}&qty=${amount}`);
                }else{
                xhttp.open('GET', `/?action=add&product_id=${productId}&qty=${amount}`);
                }

                xhttp.send();
            });
        </script>
        <script src="https://us1-config.doofinder.com/2.x/b7b9d280-7f33-4e69-8f19-741fcd073c29.js" async></script>
        <script>
            (function() {
                // Verifica si estamos en la página específica lo antes posible
                if (window.location.href.includes("/pages/contact-us/")) {
                    // Intentamos cambiar el texto lo antes posible en caso de que ya esté cargado
                    var label = document.querySelector('label.form-label[for="contact_question"]');
                    if (label) {
                        label.textContent = "Comments";
                    }

                    // Usamos MutationObserver para detectar cuando el label se agrega al DOM
                    var observer = new MutationObserver(function(mutationsList, observer) {
                        mutationsList.forEach(function(mutation) {
                            mutation.addedNodes.forEach(function(node) {
                                if (node.nodeType === 1) { // Verifica si es un elemento HTML
                                    var updatedLabel = document.querySelector('label.form-label[for="contact_question"]');
                                    if (updatedLabel) {
                                        updatedLabel.textContent = "Comments";
                                        observer.disconnect(); // Detenemos la observación una vez realizado el cambio
                                    }
                                }
                            });
                        });
                    });

                    // Observamos cambios en el cuerpo del documento
                    observer.observe(document.body, { childList: true, subtree: true });
                }
            })();
        </script>
        <script>
            document.addEventListener("DOMContentLoaded", function() {
                var pagesToHideElements = ["contact-us", "looking-for-something-else", "shop-on-mercado-libre-brazil", "shop-on-mercado-libre-argentina", "shop-on-mercado-libre-uruguay",
                                        "shop-on-mercado-libre", "shop-on-all-latin-american-stores", "shop-on-facebook-marketplace-argentina", "package-forwarding", "request-products","shop-online-on-latin-american-stores"]; // Agrega más páginas aquí

                if (pagesToHideElements.some(page => window.location.pathname.includes(page))) {
                    setTimeout(function() {
                        var banner = document.querySelector(".emthemesModez-banner");
                        if (banner) {
                            banner.style.display = "none";
                        }

                        var sidebarBlock = document.querySelector(".sidebarBlock.sidebarBlock--blog");
                        if (sidebarBlock) {
                            sidebarBlock.style.display = "none";
                        }
                        
                        var fbPage = document.querySelector(".sidebarBlock.sidebarBlock--fbPage");
                        if (fbPage) {
                            fbPage.style.display = "none";
                        }
                        var popularBrands = document.querySelector(".sidebarBlock--brands");
                        if (popularBrands) {
                            popularBrands.style.display = "none";
                        }
                    }, 800); // Espera medio segundo para asegurarse de que el elemento esté en el DOM
                }
            });

        <script>
            document.addEventListener("DOMContentLoaded", function() {
            // Verifica si la página contiene un elemento con la clase 'productView'
            if (document.querySelector('.productView')) {
                var acc = document.getElementsByClassName("accordion");
                var i;

                // Estilo CSS para el contenido del acordeón
                var stylePanel = document.createElement('style');
                stylePanel.innerHTML = `
                .panel {
                    max-height: 0;
                    overflow: hidden;
                    transition: max-height 0.1s ease-out;
                    padding-left: 20px; /* Espaciado lateral en el contenido desplegable */
                    padding-right: 20px; /* Espaciado lateral en el contenido desplegable */
                }`;
                document.head.appendChild(stylePanel);

                // Función para activar el acordeón al hacer clic en el botón
                for (i = 0; i < acc.length; i++) {
                acc[i].addEventListener("click", function() {
                    this.classList.toggle("active");
                    var panel = this.nextElementSibling;
                    if (panel.style.maxHeight){
                    panel.style.maxHeight = null;
                    } else {
                    panel.style.maxHeight = panel.scrollHeight + "px";
                    } 
                });
                }

                // Estilo CSS para el botón del acordeón
                var styleAccordion = document.createElement('style');
                styleAccordion.innerHTML = `
                .accordion {
                    background-color: #f2f2f2; /* Fondo gris clarito */
                    border-radius: 5px; /* Bordes redondeados */
                    padding: 10px 20px; /* Espaciado interno */
                    border: none; /* Sin bordes */
                    width: 100%; /* Ancho completo */
                    display: block; /* Convertir a bloque para permitir anchura máxima */
                    text-align: left;
                    cursor: pointer; /* Cambiar el cursor al puntero al pasar sobre él */
                    line-height: 30px; 
                    transition: background-color 0.3s; /* Transición suave para el cambio de color */
                }
                .accordion:hover {
                    background-color: #d9d9d9; /* Color de fondo ligeramente más oscuro al pasar el cursor */
                }`;
                document.head.appendChild(styleAccordion);
            }
            });
        </script>
        <script>
            document.addEventListener('DOMContentLoaded', function () {
            function toggleBannerByDevice() {
                const isMobile = window.matchMedia('(max-width: 768px)').matches;

                const desktopBanner = document.getElementById('emthemesModezBannersBlockBeforeDescription-desktop');
                const mobileBanner = document.getElementById('emthemesModezBannersBlockBeforeDescription-mobile');

                if (!desktopBanner || !mobileBanner) {
                // Espera y vuelve a intentar hasta 10 veces
                if (window.__bannerRetryCount === undefined) {
                    window.__bannerRetryCount = 0;
                }

                if (window.__bannerRetryCount < 10) {
                    window.__bannerRetryCount++;
                    return setTimeout(toggleBannerByDevice, 200); // Espera 200ms y reintenta
                } else {
                    console.warn('No se encontraron los banners después de varios intentos.');
                    return;
                }
                }

                desktopBanner.style.display = isMobile ? 'none' : 'block';
                mobileBanner.style.display = isMobile ? 'block' : 'none';
            }

            toggleBannerByDevice();
            window.addEventListener('resize', toggleBannerByDevice);
            });
        </script>

        <script>
            document.addEventListener("DOMContentLoaded", function() {
            function insertBanner() {
            if (window.disableRedditBanner) return;

            var target = document.querySelector('.productView-scope');
            if (target && target.parentNode) {
            var banner = document.createElement('div');
            var bannerHTML = '';

            if (window.innerWidth > 768) {
            // Desktop banner
            bannerHTML = '<img src="https://cdn11.bigcommerce.com/s-ftsflnse4o/images/stencil/original/image-manager/as-seen-on-reddit-desktop.jpg?t=1747164694" alt="Reddit banner desktop" style="width:100%; height:auto; border-radius:8px; margin:20px 0; padding-left:1.14286rem; padding-right:1.14286rem;">';
            } else {
            // Mobile banner
            bannerHTML = '<img src="https://cdn11.bigcommerce.com/s-ftsflnse4o/images/stencil/original/image-manager/as-seen-on-reddit-mobile.jpg?t=1747164695" alt="Reddit banner mobile" style="width:100%; height:auto; border-radius:8px; margin:20px 0; padding-left:2.28572rem; padding-right:2.28572rem;">';
            }

            banner.innerHTML = bannerHTML;
            target.parentNode.insertBefore(banner, target.nextSibling);
            } else {
            if (window.insertBannerRetries === undefined) {
            window.insertBannerRetries = 0;
            }
            if (window.insertBannerRetries < 10) {
            window.insertBannerRetries++;
            setTimeout(insertBanner, 300);
            }
            }
            }

            insertBanner();
            });
        </script>
